name: iPhone X
description:
Tempered glass screen protector.

Precision engineered round edges for a comfortable
grip and low visual impact.

Chemically enchanced real glass base with super
high 9H surface hardness.

Tempered construction with 0.33mm thickness.

Anti-fingerprint oleophobic coating to reduce stains
and oil marks.

Anti-shatter silicone film and adhesion system.

Comes with micro-fiber cloth, dust remover sticker and professional wet-wipes for error-proof application.

name: iPhone X
description:
Ultra-tough, heavy duty protective case.

Robust, durable polycarbonate snap-on case.
Padded corners for bump and drop protection.
Micro-dot pattern for increased holding grip.
Precision-cut TPU perimeter for enhanced force absorption.
Raised front frame for screen protection against drops.
Enlarged camera hole for optimum flash performance.
Includes screen protector against scratches.

name: iPhone X
description:
Silicone snap-on case.

Screen protection: Raised lips on the front ensures your screen is protected against hard surfaces.
Well designed openings: All ports, buttons and the camera have properly designed openings so your phone is as easy to operate as before.
Beatiful inside and out: High quality liquid silicone material for maximum grip and protection.
